data.description:
Short sale opportunity in Queen Valley, literally a 5 minute walk to the course, its's a public course!
Close to  restaurants over by the golf course and even a lake! Super nice area with view of the mountains in every direction. Home shows well - just waiting for the right buyer. check with your lender but I think this home could very easily go FHA.
Thank you
